ensure_unique(rnlcn_filt)
ts_plotly_regional(
  rnlcn_filt,
  var_label  = get_var_label("RNLCN", labels),
  unit_label = get_unit_label(rnlcn_filt$UNIT[1], labels)
)
```

#### Ore lavorate

```{r}
#| label: lab-ts-rnlht

# 6. RNLHT -----

rnlht_filt <- filter_data(rnlht, unit = "THS")
ensure_unique(rnlht_filt)
ts_plotly_regional(
  rnlht_filt,
  var_label  = get_var_label("RNLHT", labels),
  unit_label = get_unit_label("THS", labels)
)
```

:::

### Column {width="40%"}

```{r}
