# Reddito e compensi

```{r}
#| label: inc-load
#| include: false

# 1. Load income and compensation variables once -----

ruwcd <- load_variable("RUWCD")
rowcd <- load_variable("ROWCD")
```

## Row {height="100px"}

```{r}
#| label: inc-vb1
#| content: valuebox
#| title: "Compensi correnti (Lombardia)"

# 1. Value box: RUWCD MIO_EUR, ITC4, latest year -----

